div.div:
score :
- inclusive keywords count in title >= 1 ? +1
- inclusive keywords count in description >= 1 ? +1
- inclusive keywords count in topic(s) >= 1 ? +1
- inclusive keywords count in readme file(s) >= 1 ? +1
- service(s) directory(ies) count >= 1 ? +1
- service(s) file(s) count >= 1 ? +1
- docker-compose file(s) count >= 1 ? +1
- service(s) in docker-compose file(s) count >= 1 ? +1
- database(s) in docker-compose file(s) count >= 1 ? +1
heuristics :
docker-compose file(s) >= 1
&& service(s) in docker-compose file(s) count >= 1
&& count of inclusive keywords in title, description, topics, readme>= 1
&& database(s) in docker-compose file(s) count >= 1
&& service(s) in docker-compose file(s) count > database(s) in docker-compose file(s) count
&& score >= 1
